{"tid":1234543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】6.12肺癌大叔被上門搜證擬改控暴動罪 女兒求影片證父清白","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:41:31.000Z","uid":241327,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"1b95773eea9cc13c46958215ce6bb1739663a0d5","tid":1234543,"uid":241327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，唔係好知規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過想大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190617/59724245?fbclid=IwAR1QUxhqXJtZuihEhNh6I0KzBtfEeYUitTF2NJH93o9tGDktY5bHvGoi9G8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59724245%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1QUxhqXJtZuihEhNh6I0KzBtfEeYUitTF2NJH93o9tGDktY5bHvGoi9G8&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=504f0291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59724245%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1QUxhqXJtZuihEhNh6I0KzBtfEeYUitTF2NJH93o9tGDktY5bHvGoi9G8&h=aef90c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190617/59724245?fbclid=IwAR1QUxhqXJtZuihEhNh6I0KzBtfEeYUitTF2NJH93o9tGDktY5bHvGoi9G8</a><br />\n<br />\n患有肺癌三期的中槍大叔「老吳」，在6.12被警察用橡膠子彈射中後被捕，其故事令不少人為之動容，6.16響應他的呼籲上街。不過其女兒Francis表示，早前父親被控非法集會罪，得悉警方正申請搜查令搜屋，欲搜集更多證據改控暴動罪。Francis呼籲當日假如有人拍攝到父親中槍一刻並作為證據，更能證明警方在無受威脅情況下開槍。<br />\n<br />\n女兒Francis轉述爸爸的話，當時只是用粗口罵警察，手上並無武器，不是在衝擊防線，警察根本在沒有受任何生命威脅的情況下開槍。目前家人已找到人證，證明他中槍一刻的過程沒有使用暴力，但律師認為如有影片證供更為穩妥，故她呼籲當日有拍攝影片的現場人士，如6.12下午5時30分，在添美道附近有拍攝到父親中槍一刻，請透過電郵聯絡Francis。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡電郵：fightforgreenman@gmail.com"},{"pid":"0e87bc81774068164b948e694e17af087575b819","tid":1234543,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3